      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "我都有些害怕了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "16:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "万一你以后乱说话惹了事，不会连累我吧？",
